# Astro Portfolio Project

## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Astro 5 (static output)
- **UI:** React 19 with `@astrojs/react`
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 4 via `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin
- **Components:** `@cloudflare/kumo` (UI library), `@phosphor-icons/react` (icons)
- **Deployment:** Cloudflare Workers (static assets) — see `wrangler.jsonc`

## Project Structure

- `src/pages/` — Astro pages (`.astro`)
- `src/components/` — React components (`.tsx`) hydrated with `client:visible`
- `src/layouts/` — Astro layouts
- `src/styles/global.css` — Global styles, Tailwind imports, Kumo theme
- `public/` — Static assets served as-is

## Important Notes

- React components use `client:visible` for hydration — they render on the client only when visible in viewport
- Tailwind is configured as a Vite plugin, not as an Astro integration
- Kumo CSS is imported in `global.css` via `@import "@cloudflare/kumo/styles/tailwind"` and source scanning via `@source`
